Objective:
The objective of this project is to develop a system that allows users to register, log in, and manage their profile information efficiently.
Scope:
•	User Registration
•	User Login
•	Profile Management
Stakeholders:
•	End Users
•	Business Team
•	Development Team
•	QA Team
Business Requirements:
1.	The system should allow users to register using email and password.
2.	The system should validate user input fields.
3.	The system should allow users to log in securely.
4.	The system should allow users to update profile details.
5.	The system should display appropriate error and success messages.
Assumptions:
•	Users have a valid email address.
•	Internet connectivity is available.
Constraints:
•	Basic security validations only (for demo purpose).

